{"tid":1733382,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"6s叉電愈叉愈少，點解會咁？（免費幫各位手足整iphone","createTime":"2019-11-18T05:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T06:55:49.000Z","uid":320119,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e5ea11f4927e4f74c29106c4292edfd39a253e","tid":1733382,"uid":320119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"我p牌推唔到舊post，唔知我係邊個既巴絲可以睇番：<br />\n專門整iPhone壞主板之你問我答（義士免費整iPhone)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559974</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有位手足部6s愈叉愈少電，我幫佢整<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOGeFV5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOGeFV5.png&h=7e2409f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先檢查下，電流表顯示叉電電流只有500毫安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而電話係有顯示叉電<br />\n說明係有電入到去，不過電流好低好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n插電腦亦都無反應<br />\n同時出現呢兩個問題<br />\n懷疑係負責叉電同埋聯電腦既usb ic 問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bAopiPt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbAopiPt.png&h=f6d5ef40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢粒就係usb ic<br />\n換粒新既usb ic落去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZ5OLuN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZ5OLuN.png&h=e8319919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裝番機測試<br />\n電流去到2.1安<br />\n呢個就係正常既叉電電流<br />\n聯電腦都有番反應<br />\n咁就可以正常使用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇落好似好嚴重出現兩個問題<br />\n其實只要熟悉iphone 工作原理，好簡單好快就會維修好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整機既巴打絲打可以ig或tg聯絡我，<span style=\"color: red;\">一律免費</span><br />\nIg: iphonemotherboardhk <br />\nTg:<a href=\"https://t.me/IphoneMotherboardhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FIphoneMotherboardhk&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2Wg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=c975da0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/IphoneMotherboardhk</a>"},{"pid":"9ec5c9baf26c499839af4507e61ab6e6ce5470ee","tid":1733382,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc71fb01ddf5a2907590565b5e574ebd6613108","tid":1733382,"uid":320119,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9ec5c9baf26c499839af4507e61ab6e6ce5470ee","tid":1733382,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"巴打今次我無用支那字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cef5c91c9444849d5933d443ea73397a5b87917","tid":1733382,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc71fb01ddf5a2907590565b5e574ebd6613108","tid":1733382,"uid":320119,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9ec5c9baf26c499839af4507e61ab6e6ce5470ee","tid":1733382,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"巴打今次我無用支那字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src